txt.en: The leader of the Scholar's Guild has asked to draught a Morgul Leadership Analysis Report for the Rangers encamped in Minas Morgul.
The crafting recipes you must create can be bartered for from the Improved Recipes vendor.\n\nDraught a Morgul Leadership Analysis Report.
Execute the recipe for a Morgul Leadership Analysis Report

'Oh this is—how can our enemy be this disorganized and still make life so difficult for us? Look at this!'

The Guild Leader waves a piece of paper in your face.

'These intercepted orders just say 'Kill 10 men'. Hardly a strategy. Go find me evidence of a competent leader among their ranks. There has to be one somewhere.'
Executed the recipe for Morgul Leadership Analysis Report

'Oh this is—how can our enemy be this disorganized and still make life so difficult for us? Look at this!'
